{
  "id": "699e7cf9c23a8eed25eb0bad",
  "title": "#inajob の試しに録音してみた talk138: 5歳の娘と伊豆大島旅行",
  "created": 1771994364,
  "updated": 1772037394,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "699e7cf9c23a8eed25eb0bad",
      "text": "#inajob の試しに録音してみた talk138: 5歳の娘と伊豆大島旅行",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771994364,
      "updated": 1771994364
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1de40000000000126173",
      "text": "[https://open.spotify.com/episode/4lFFGFfnIu0HKnd0HzAl2m]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035557,
      "updated": 1772035562
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1de50000000000126174",
      "text": "\t[Google Formsで感想を送る https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1fC9gUB6PC3uJidZAJ8pgD1qLiMdvIgZOenrTwcOqpnw/]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035558,
      "updated": 1772037392
    },
    {
      "id": "699f251000000000008d341f",
      "text": " [Discordサーバー「inajob川」に参加する https://discord.gg/vHu4CXuMPq]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037392,
      "updated": 1772037392
    },
    {
      "id": "699f251000000000008d3420",
      "text": " \t[参加する前に様子を見る https://inajob.github.io/inajob-river-peeker/]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037392,
      "updated": 1772037392
    },
    {
      "id": "699f251000000000008d3421",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037392,
      "updated": 1772037392
    },
    {
      "id": "699e7cfb00000000006975f2",
      "text": "\t健康",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771994364,
      "updated": 1772037394
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1afb000000000012616b",
      "text": "\t\tまぁ健康",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772034811,
      "updated": 1772034814
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1e1c0000000000126175",
      "text": "\t\t花粉については無策",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035613,
      "updated": 1772035620
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1b02000000000012616c",
      "text": "\t旅行の準備",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772034819,
      "updated": 1772034851
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1b840000000000126172",
      "text": "\t\t正月の沖縄旅行から帰ってきてしばらくしたころ（1月下旬）あたりに計画を始める",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772034949,
      "updated": 1772034974
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1e590000000000126176",
      "text": "\t\t伊豆大島はちょいちょい旅先の候補には上がるが行ったことが無かった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035673,
      "updated": 1772035691
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1e710000000000126177",
      "text": "\t\t他の候補",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035697,
      "updated": 1772035699
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1e730000000000126178",
      "text": "\t\t\tウィンタースポーツ？",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035699,
      "updated": 1772035702
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1e790000000000126179",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t初動が遅くてホテルの確保が難しそう・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035705,
      "updated": 1772035722
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1e92000000000012617a",
      "text": "\t\t予約系",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035730,
      "updated": 1772035735
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1f1c0000000000126186",
      "text": "\t\t\tオフシーズン気味なので予約しやすかったように思う",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035868,
      "updated": 1772035891
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1e96000000000012617b",
      "text": "\t\t\tホテル",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035735,
      "updated": 1772035736
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1eaa000000000012617f",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t多分前日とかでも予約できたように思う",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035755,
      "updated": 1772035766
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1e98000000000012617c",
      "text": "\t\t\t船",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035736,
      "updated": 1772035739
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1eb60000000000126180",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこちらも前日でも予約出来そうだった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035767,
      "updated": 1772035779
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1ee20000000000126183",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tジェット船と大型客船がある",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035810,
      "updated": 1772035815
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1eee0000000000126184",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t小型の飛行機という手もある",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035822,
      "updated": 1772035827
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1e9a000000000012617d",
      "text": "\t\t\tレンタカー",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035739,
      "updated": 1772035742
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1ea1000000000012617e",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tこれが一番面倒だった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035745,
      "updated": 1772035783
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1ec70000000000126181",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\tインターネットから予約できる店が非常に少ない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035783,
      "updated": 1772035790
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1ece0000000000126182",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t電話予約も2社断られて3社目で予約できた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035790,
      "updated": 1772035807
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1efe0000000000126185",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tもう少し子供が大きくなるとレンタサイクルとかでも良いかも",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035839,
      "updated": 1772035851
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1b0c000000000012616d",
      "text": "\t1日目",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772034828,
      "updated": 1772034840
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1b5c0000000000126170",
      "text": "\t\t移動日",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772034909,
      "updated": 1772034910
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1f510000000000126188",
      "text": "\t\tでかいスーツケースが便利",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035921,
      "updated": 1772035926
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1f5b0000000000126189",
      "text": "\t\t\t都会の移動はケースのタイヤで問題なく転がせる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035931,
      "updated": 1772035944
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1f68000000000012618a",
      "text": "\t\t\tレンタカーにそのまま積み込める",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035944,
      "updated": 1772035950
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1f6e000000000012618b",
      "text": "\t\t\t疲れた娘を乗せることもできなくはない（危ない）",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035950,
      "updated": 1772035960
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1b5f0000000000126171",
      "text": "\t\t13:30発のジェット船で島に向かう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772034911,
      "updated": 1772035917
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1f7b000000000012618c",
      "text": "\t\tジェット船",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035963,
      "updated": 1772035966
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1f7e000000000012618d",
      "text": "\t\t\t足が出てきて若干浮きながら進む船",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035966,
      "updated": 1772035975
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1f86000000000012618e",
      "text": "\t\t\t座席は飛行機のような感じで、基本シートベルトを付けて座り続ける必要がある",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035975,
      "updated": 1772035993
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1f99000000000012618f",
      "text": "\t\t\t甲板に出るとかはできない",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772035993,
      "updated": 1772035997
    },
    {
      "id": "699f20aa00000000001261a1",
      "text": "\t\t\t大型海洋生物警戒海域航行中 というアラートが出ていて面白かった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036266,
      "updated": 1772036284
    },
    {
      "id": "699f24eb00000000008d341b",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t>[https://x.com/ina_ani/status/2025130550055551000 @ina_ani]: 「大型海洋生物警戒海域航行中」",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037355,
      "updated": 1772037357
    },
    {
      "id": "699f24ed00000000008d341c",
      "text": "    >ヤバそうな表示!!(いつも出るやつだと思う)",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037357,
      "updated": 1772037357
    },
    {
      "id": "699f24ed00000000008d341d",
      "text": "    >[https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HBq1gLrbYAAwE4l.jpg]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037357,
      "updated": 1772037357
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1fa90000000000126190",
      "text": "\t\tホテル",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036009,
      "updated": 1772036011
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1fb00000000000126192",
      "text": "\t\t\t研修施設を流用した「アットホーム」そうなホテル",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036017,
      "updated": 1772036032
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1fc60000000000126193",
      "text": "\t\t\t玄関ロビーが非常にごちゃごちゃと機材が転がっており、広いスペースの端にこたつが置いてある",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036038,
      "updated": 1772036070
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1fe80000000000126194",
      "text": "\t\t\tロビーに釣りたての生魚が転がっている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036072,
      "updated": 1772036092
    },
    {
      "id": "699f24d600000000008d3418",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t>[https://x.com/ina_ani/status/2025165790694220096 @ina_ani]: ホテルの玄関から入ると、これが床に転がってる…",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037334,
      "updated": 1772037337
    },
    {
      "id": "699f24d900000000008d3419",
      "text": "    >[https://pbs.twimg.com/media/HBrVjKea8AABXih.jpg]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037337,
      "updated": 1772037337
    },
    {
      "id": "699f20020000000000126195",
      "text": "\t\t\tなんだこのホテル！",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036098,
      "updated": 1772036102
    },
    {
      "id": "699f200c0000000000126196",
      "text": "\t\t\t5歳の娘はすぐに打ち解けて、上記こたつに入り込みオリンピックをテレビで見ていた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036108,
      "updated": 1772036125
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1faa0000000000126191",
      "text": "\t\t\t実質貸し切り",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036011,
      "updated": 1772036013
    },
    {
      "id": "699f20230000000000126197",
      "text": "\t\t\t親戚のおじいちゃん・おばあちゃんの家に行ったという感じ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036131,
      "updated": 1772036148
    },
    {
      "id": "699f20410000000000126198",
      "text": "\t\t露天風呂 元町浜の湯",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036161,
      "updated": 1772036174
    },
    {
      "id": "699f204e0000000000126199",
      "text": "\t\t\t水着着用の混浴露天風呂",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036174,
      "updated": 1772036188
    },
    {
      "id": "699f205c000000000012619a",
      "text": "\t\t\t夕日が沈むのを見ることが出来る",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036188,
      "updated": 1772036195
    },
    {
      "id": "699f2066000000000012619b",
      "text": "\t\t\tかろうじて富士山も見えた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036198,
      "updated": 1772036203
    },
    {
      "id": "699f2072000000000012619c",
      "text": "\t\t夕食",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036211,
      "updated": 1772036215
    },
    {
      "id": "699f2076000000000012619d",
      "text": "\t\t\tロビーに転がっていた魚が調理されて登場 おいしかった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036215,
      "updated": 1772036229
    },
    {
      "id": "699f2085000000000012619e",
      "text": "\t\t\t子供向けにはオムレツを作ってくれてありがたかった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036229,
      "updated": 1772036238
    },
    {
      "id": "699f2091000000000012619f",
      "text": "\t\t星空体験",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036241,
      "updated": 1772036244
    },
    {
      "id": "699f209400000000001261a0",
      "text": "\t\t\tホテルの周りが真っ暗で非常に綺麗な星空が見えた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036244,
      "updated": 1772036255
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1b17000000000012616e",
      "text": "\t2日目",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772034840,
      "updated": 1772034841
    },
    {
      "id": "699f20c600000000001261a2",
      "text": "\t\t朝の散歩",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036294,
      "updated": 1772036297
    },
    {
      "id": "699f20da00000000001261a5",
      "text": "\t\t\t火山岩の観察",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036315,
      "updated": 1772036319
    },
    {
      "id": "699f20c900000000001261a3",
      "text": "\t\t朝食",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036297,
      "updated": 1772036301
    },
    {
      "id": "699f20ea00000000001261a6",
      "text": "\t\t\t余ったご飯をおにぎりにさせてもらう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036331,
      "updated": 1772036338
    },
    {
      "id": "699f20cc00000000001261a4",
      "text": "\t\t三原山登山",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036301,
      "updated": 1772036303
    },
    {
      "id": "699f20fb00000000001261a8",
      "text": "\t\t\tなるべく歩きたくないので最短ルートを選択（片道1-2時間)",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036347,
      "updated": 1772036368
    },
    {
      "id": "699f211c00000000001261a9",
      "text": "\t\t\tベビーカーを押してでも登頂できるというルートなので、道はきれいだった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036381,
      "updated": 1772036397
    },
    {
      "id": "699f212e00000000001261aa",
      "text": "\t\t\tお鉢巡りはせずに、火口をみるだけで下山",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036398,
      "updated": 1772036417
    },
    {
      "id": "699f217000000000001261ae",
      "text": "\t\t\tおにぎりはここで食す",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036465,
      "updated": 1772036468
    },
    {
      "id": "699f214300000000001261ab",
      "text": "\t\t\t登山口の博物館的なところにも訪問した",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036420,
      "updated": 1772036428
    },
    {
      "id": "699f214c00000000001261ac",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t登山インストラクターの方が5歳の娘に丁寧に接してくれて、娘も満足した様子",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036429,
      "updated": 1772036449
    },
    {
      "id": "699f216700000000001261ad",
      "text": "\t\t昼ご飯",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036455,
      "updated": 1772036460
    },
    {
      "id": "699f217600000000001261af",
      "text": "\t\t\t（おにぎりだけではおなかが空いたので・・）",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036470,
      "updated": 1772036480
    },
    {
      "id": "699f217f00000000001261b0",
      "text": "\t\t\t島に移住してきた人が経営するお店",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036480,
      "updated": 1772036488
    },
    {
      "id": "699f218a00000000001261b1",
      "text": "\t\t\t移住した人の話、昔から島にいる人（ホテルの方々）の話の両方を聞くことが出来た",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036491,
      "updated": 1772036519
    },
    {
      "id": "699f21a900000000001261b2",
      "text": "\t\t公園",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036521,
      "updated": 1772036526
    },
    {
      "id": "699f21b200000000001261b3",
      "text": "\t\t\t娘の希望にて・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036530,
      "updated": 1772036533
    },
    {
      "id": "699f21b700000000001261b4",
      "text": "\t\t温泉 御神火温泉（ごじんか）",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036535,
      "updated": 1772036553
    },
    {
      "id": "699f21b800000000001261b5",
      "text": "\t\t天候が悪くなる・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036536,
      "updated": 1772036560
    },
    {
      "id": "699f21d500000000001261b6",
      "text": "\t\tテレビをつけているとご飯を食べない5歳の娘",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036565,
      "updated": 1772036573
    },
    {
      "id": "699f21dd00000000001261b7",
      "text": "\t\t\t自分から「切って」と言い出していた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036573,
      "updated": 1772036585
    },
    {
      "id": "699f21ea00000000001261b8",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tわかっていても見ちゃうんだろうなぁ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036586,
      "updated": 1772036591
    },
    {
      "id": "699f1b19000000000012616f",
      "text": "\t3日目",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772034841,
      "updated": 1772034843
    },
    {
      "id": "699f220100000000001261b9",
      "text": "\t\t天気が悪い日",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036609,
      "updated": 1772036613
    },
    {
      "id": "699f220c00000000001261ba",
      "text": "\t\t伊豆大島ミュージアム ジオノス",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036620,
      "updated": 1772036620
    },
    {
      "id": "699f220c00000000001261bb",
      "text": "\t\t\t急ぎ目に見て回った",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036620,
      "updated": 1772036626
    },
    {
      "id": "699f221700000000001261bc",
      "text": "\t\tぱれ・らめーる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036632,
      "updated": 1772036632
    },
    {
      "id": "699f221800000000001261bd",
      "text": "\t\t\t貝殻の博物館",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036632,
      "updated": 1772036636
    },
    {
      "id": "699f224b00000000001261c2",
      "text": "\t\t\t教室3個分くらいのスペースに貝殻がずらりと並べられていた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036683,
      "updated": 1772036696
    },
    {
      "id": "699f221c00000000001261be",
      "text": "\t\t\t妻・娘にも好評だった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036636,
      "updated": 1772036641
    },
    {
      "id": "699f222800000000001261bf",
      "text": "\t\t地層切断面",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036650,
      "updated": 1772036654
    },
    {
      "id": "699f222e00000000001261c0",
      "text": "\t\t\tバームクーヘンのような地形",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036654,
      "updated": 1772036658
    },
    {
      "id": "699f226400000000001261c3",
      "text": "\t\t朝の時点でジェット船の航行予定が△、そして×に・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036709,
      "updated": 1772036743
    },
    {
      "id": "699f24ba00000000008d3416",
      "text": "\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/3709052d396ce89210183ba056cbbc01]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037306,
      "updated": 1772037308
    },
    {
      "id": "699f228800000000001261c5",
      "text": "\t\t\t大型客船に振替が発生",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036744,
      "updated": 1772036756
    },
    {
      "id": "699f229700000000001261c6",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t電話・インターネットからはどうにもならなく、港に早めに向かう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036760,
      "updated": 1772036773
    },
    {
      "id": "699f22bb00000000001261c7",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t自由席というか、もう席は無いけど詰め込んで行くということらしい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036795,
      "updated": 1772036816
    },
    {
      "id": "699f22da00000000001261c8",
      "text": "\t\t\t1.5時間のはずが、5時間の船旅に・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036827,
      "updated": 1772036837
    },
    {
      "id": "699f22e700000000001261c9",
      "text": "\t\t大型客船",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036839,
      "updated": 1772036844
    },
    {
      "id": "699f22eb00000000001261ca",
      "text": "\t\t\t満員とはいっても、天気が良くなったので、甲板で過ごせば全然スペースには余裕があった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036844,
      "updated": 1772036874
    },
    {
      "id": "699f230a00000000001261cb",
      "text": "\t\t\t室内で過ごしたい人は、廊下の片側に座り込む感じになっていた・・",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036874,
      "updated": 1772036889
    },
    {
      "id": "699f232100000000001261cc",
      "text": "\t\t\t船の中の探検",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036897,
      "updated": 1772036906
    },
    {
      "id": "699f232b00000000001261cd",
      "text": "\t\t\t何グループかの人と仲良くなる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036907,
      "updated": 1772036918
    },
    {
      "id": "699f233500000000001261ce",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tRPG・アドベンチャーゲームっぽい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036918,
      "updated": 1772036923
    },
    {
      "id": "699f233b00000000001261cf",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t登場人物が限られており、その人たちは大体同じ場所にいる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036923,
      "updated": 1772036937
    },
    {
      "id": "699f234d00000000001261d0",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t家族ぐるみで旅行に気他グループの子供たちの輪に混ぜてもらう",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036941,
      "updated": 1772036955
    },
    {
      "id": "699f235b00000000001261d1",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t結果5人ほどの子供を束ねて面倒を見ていた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036956,
      "updated": 1772036963
    },
    {
      "id": "699f237400000000001261d2",
      "text": "\t\t\t夕焼けがきれい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036981,
      "updated": 1772036985
    },
    {
      "id": "699f237d00000000001261d4",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t一度沈んだ太陽が、また出てきたりして面白かった",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036989,
      "updated": 1772036999
    },
    {
      "id": "699f237a00000000001261d3",
      "text": "\t\t\t夜景がきれい",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036986,
      "updated": 1772036988
    },
    {
      "id": "699f239000000000001261d5",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t東京湾",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037008,
      "updated": 1772037009
    },
    {
      "id": "699f239400000000001261d6",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t羽田空港に着陸する飛行機がいい感じに見えた",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037012,
      "updated": 1772037026
    },
    {
      "id": "699f23a900000000001261d7",
      "text": "\t\t\t\tレインボーブリッジの下をくぐる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037033,
      "updated": 1772037037
    },
    {
      "id": "699f24a100000000008d3414",
      "text": "\t\t\t\t\t[https://gyazo.com/db6abb140cfe7a9744ca36daf3631b69]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037282,
      "updated": 1772037285
    },
    {
      "id": "699f23c300000000001261d9",
      "text": "\t\t\t結果として大型客船の方がジェット船より良かった気がする",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037060,
      "updated": 1772037110
    },
    {
      "id": "699f23da00000000001261da",
      "text": "\t総括",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037110,
      "updated": 1772037110
    },
    {
      "id": "699f23ff00000000001261db",
      "text": "\t\t今回の旅行のプランは[inajob.icon]がほぼ考えたので、主催者側としての旅の楽しみが出来た",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037119,
      "updated": 1772037140
    },
    {
      "id": "699f241400000000001261dc",
      "text": "\t\t\t参加者が楽しめているのを見て、自分も良い気持ちになる",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037141,
      "updated": 1772037171
    },
    {
      "id": "699f243300000000001261dd",
      "text": "\t\t旅のオーナーシップを感じている",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037171,
      "updated": 1772037180
    },
    {
      "id": "699f243c00000000001261de",
      "text": "\t\t\t仕事でも良く言われるやつ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037180,
      "updated": 1772037188
    },
    {
      "id": "699f244800000000001261df",
      "text": "\t\tオフシーズンに訪れる事の良さ",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772037192,
      "updated": 1772037205
    },
    {
      "id": "699f223700000000001261c1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1772036664,
      "updated": 1772036664
    },
    {
      "id": "699e7d0100000000006975f4",
      "text": "\t前回 [#inajob の試しに録音してみた talk137: Gemini Proに律速される生活・北風と太陽的な学習・今しか楽しめない遊び]",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771994369,
      "updated": 1771994388
    },
    {
      "id": "699e7d0200000000006975f5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58442db3ee4a2400116eb406",
      "created": 1771994371,
      "updated": 1771994371
    }
  ]
}